1 GAM

1.1 Введение

1.1.1 Полиномы

\(y_i = \sum_{j=0}^k \beta_j \times x^j_i + \epsilon_i = \beta_0 \times x^0_0 + \beta_1 \times x^1_i + ... \beta_k \times x^k_i + \epsilon_i\)

set.seed(42)
poly_2 <- tibble(x = 1:100,
                 y = 4*x + 8*x^2+rnorm(100, sd = 5000))

poly_2 %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x, y))+
  geom_point()

poly_2_fit1 <- lm(y ~ poly(x, 2, raw = TRUE), data = poly_2)
poly_2_fit2 <- lm(y ~ x+I(x^2), data = poly_2)

summary(poly_2_fit1)

  geom_point()+
  geom_line(data = poly_2_fit2_values, aes(x = x, y = fit), color = "blue")+
  labs(caption = poly_2_fit2$call)

1.2 GAM

poly_2_fit4 <- gam(y ~ s(x), data = poly_2)
summary(poly_2_fit4)

                 fit = poly_2_fit4$fitted.values)

poly_2 %>% 
  ggplot(aes(x, y))+
  geom_point()+
  geom_line(data = fitted, aes(x = x, y = fit), color = "blue")+
  labs(caption = poly_2_fit4$call)
